    "description": "本課程主要內容為多媒體整合於互動網頁設計學習，分為兩個階段─「網頁介面設計」與「多媒體互動設計」，並著重在於此兩階段相關軟體和平台資源的傳授。<br><br>The content of the course is multimedia integration in interactive web design. The course is divided into two phases - \"web interface design\" and \"multimedia interactive design\" and focuses on the teaching of the related software and platform resources.<br><br>",
